&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for a Designer to join our London team and work across both marketing and product design. This is a generalist role; one week you might be designing a landing page, the next you&#39;re designing UI for The Modo Energy Terminal platform or creating assets for a conference stand.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We move fast and have strong product opinions; what we need is someone who can bring those to life beautifully, and over time help us raise the bar on craft and design thinking across the company.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll sit within the Product Operations team as an early designer hire, with direct cross-functional touch points across product and engineering. This is an entry to mid-level role with real room to grow: Modo is still early and the design function is being built, which means your work will have outsized impact from day one.&lt;/p&gt;
