&lt;li&gt;Comfortable working across both marketing and product design&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fast, autonomous, and able to context-switch between different types of work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A genuine eye for detail and a high personal bar for quality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enthusiasm for learning about energy and the world of BESS, solar, and wind - no prior knowledge needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to have&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
