&lt;p&gt;You will produce written articles, videos, and research outputs that make complex market dynamics easier to understand. Your work will help developers, owners, operators, investors, and lenders understand how batteries earn revenue, how market conditions are changing, and what that means commercially.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A large part of the role is building Modo Energy’s AI-native research capability. That means using large language models, AI coding assistants, automations, and data pipelines to turn market data into high-quality analysis faster than traditional approaches allow. We are looking for someone who already uses AI to improve how they work, and who wants to keep pushing that further.&lt;/p&gt;
